revision.text:
{{Documentation subpage}}
<!-- Please place template categories where indicated at the bottom of this page and interwikis at Wikidata (see [[Wikipedia:Wikidata]]) -->
This template generates an external link from a [[persistent identifier]] for materials within the [[NDL Digital Collections]] to its metadata entry in NDL Search, a part of the [[National Diet Library]] of Japan.

== Usage ==
Input [[persistent identifier]] (PID) as parameter 1, which is always required. For example, for PID <code><nowiki>888725</nowiki></code>:
*input: <code><nowiki>{{NDLPID|888725}}</nowiki></code>
*and get output: <samp>{{NDLPID|888725}}</samp>

== See also ==
{{Wikidata property|P9836}}
* {{tl|NDLDC}}
* {{tl|doi}}/{{tl|doi-inline}} with prefix: 10.11501, e.g, {{doi|10.11501/888725}} which is virtually the same as {{NDLDC|format=pid|888725}}, however not all NDLDC PIDs have DOIs
* {{tl|JPNO}}
* {{tl|JACAR}}
* {{tl|NAID}}
* {{tl|NCID}}
* {{tl|Catalog lookup link}}

== External links ==
* [https://ndlsearch.ndl.go.jp/en/ NDL Search]
* [https://dl.ndl.go.jp/en/ NDL Digital Collections]
* {{cite web| url=https://www.ndl.go.jp/en/dlib/standards/lod/uri.html#uri01-2 |title=IDs assigned to metadata of digital contents (NDL Metadata ID) |work=Uniform Resource Identifiers (URI) for National Diet Library resources |series=Digital Library Projects |publisher=National Diet Library}}


